    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, I thought I\u2019d keep this beauty forever, but life has other plans. She\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every weekend, and she truly looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior still has that fresh feel, and she drives as smooth as silk. There might be a tiny, tiny mark if you look with a magnifying glass, but you\u2019d have to really hunt for it! I'm looking for a fellow enthusiast who will appreciate her as much as I do. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
