      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level specimen with a meticulously optimized drivetrain. This unit features a Stage 2 remapped ECU paired with a high-flow intake system for peak volumetric efficiency. The suspension geometry has been dialed in with adjustable coilovers, ensuring zero-lash steering response and neutral handling through the apex. Every fluid has been flushed with high-performance synthetic, and the compression across all cylinders remains within factory tolerances. The paintwork has been treated with a multi-stage correction and ceramic coating, resulting in a mirror finish that matches the mechanical integrity. This is a turnkey machine for the discerning pilot who demands uncompromising power delivery and chassis rigidity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
